{"tid":687810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【18歲卜卜脆】東瀛女拳手睇得又打得 鍾情李小龍","createTime":"2018-06-02T14:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T05:05:43.000Z","uid":112551,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d9efa6a0dbf77ce05ae8f505a169d55296b89b8a","tid":687810,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"真是18歲，卜卜脆，講的是第一次來到香港打比賽的18歲大學生拳手鈴木菜奈子（Nanako Suzuki），今日在同為拳手的母親陪同下，從東京飛到香港會見傳媒。這位除了擁有kawai的可愛面龐外，還要是香港傳奇李小龍的頭號粉絲，她穿着的打拳bra top背後還印有李小龍名句「Don&rsquo;t think, feel」的字句，打拳褲更印有一條龍，加上可愛笑容，下月14日到修頓室內場出戰DEF舉辧的Road to Glory II比賽，一定俘擄不少男粉絲，今日連星如師弟潘啟情也被這位「少女拳手」弄得臉紅紅。<br />\n<br />\n鈴木菜奈子母親都是拳手，今日跟囡囡到場但就拒絕合照，4歲開始學習「極真空手道」的菜奈子說，自己對已故巨星李小龍是「一見鍾情」，她說：「我第一套睇李小龍的戲是《死亡遊戲》，是在屋企睇的，我自細好鍾意李小龍這種好型、打得好犀利、又表現好strong的人。」難怪她的bra top印了李小龍名句，只是少了一個逗號「Don&rsquo;t think feel」。<br />\n2年前從空手道改行到打西洋拳的菜奈子，是前拳王河野公平的同門師妹，本來對手是香港的林海明，但她因要應付大學考試，所以棄戰，改由泰拳轉打西洋拳的黃嘉欣，在職業拳賽錄得一勝一負，菜奈子說：「今次是我第一次到香港比賽，又緊張又期待，去年第二場職業賽我輸在距離感不夠好，希望能有助我下月在香港比賽中獲勝，令更多人認識我。」雖然有kawai的笑臉，但菜奈子坦言不介意打拳得來的傷瘀。<br />\n記者/攝影：徐嘉華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527935624_2592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527935624_2592.jpg&h=5762ce58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527935630_628f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527935630_628f.jpg&h=9ec6c43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527944047_1866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527944047_1866.jpg&h=8985fc92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌... 真係好可愛好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  戀愛了<br />\n我要學日文!"},{"pid":"2b0857d9d2a5016892a3ed7f64649d2ebb49c390","tid":687810,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f99281341f137b8d81c9586964b21b2d0c638b8","tid":687810,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oriO1JvXqiSdpuGMU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oriO1JvXqiSdpuGMU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=caa06c67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oriO1JvXqiSdpuGMU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oriO1JvXqiSdpuGMU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=caa06c67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe545a983fc4758ac6696565413de35a2ac16f10","tid":687810,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"再靚少少可以溝我"},{"pid":"5db889112fd82ad502f444a465eed3341d435d23","tid":687810,"uid":57835,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fe545a983fc4758ac6696565413de35a2ac16f10","tid":687810,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"再靚少少可以溝我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"你以為有得你屌？"},{"pid":"215c233eace051760367b29b36ebe3a0fb53a90b","tid":687810,"uid":6717,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5db889112fd82ad502f444a465eed3341d435d23","tid":687810,"uid":57835,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fe545a983fc4758ac6696565413de35a2ac16f10","tid":687810,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"再靚少少可以溝我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:44:14.000Z","msg":"你以為有得你屌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"